        <abstract> 
<p>Bad news about <hi rend="italic">Kosmos</hi> [ceasing publication].</p> 
            <p>Fritz Müller’s losses [in a flood]; "I have long looked on him as the best observer in the world."</p>
            <p>EK’s astonishing account of crustacean that repairs its legs in an ancestral form seems to support Pangenesis, which has hardly any friends.</p>
        </abstract>
